qas.question: What year marked the end of Schwarzenegger's second term in the governor's office?
What political party did Schwarzenegger belong to?
What date marked the start of Schwarzenegger's second gubernatorial term?

context: As a <a1_0>Republican<a1_0/>, he was first elected on October 7, 2003, in a special recall election to replace then-Governor <a2_0>Gray Davis<a2_0/>. Schwarzenegger was sworn in on November 17, to serve the remainder of Davis's term. Schwarzenegger was then re-elected on November 7, 2006, in California's 2006 gubernatorial election, to serve a full term as governor, defeating Democrat Phil Angelides, who was California State Treasurer at the time. Schwarzenegger was sworn in for his second term on <a3_0>January 5, 2007<a3_0/>. In <a0_0>2011<a0_0/>, Schwarzenegger completed his second term as governor.
